Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:09.35,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Travel through a thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:11.31,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Years swim through the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:14.69,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Find my body floating in time and space
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:18.31,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}From a land so wild and so desolate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:22.07,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}One more inch I'll be reaching the moon's gate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:25.40,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}In and out I breathe as time passes by
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:28.95,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Here today comes the sentence of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.09,0:22:32.41,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}What's the burning question you are seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:37.21,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}What exactly do you still want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:43.21,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Done done
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:45.09,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Look how tiny you are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.93,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Look how fragile you are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:48.72,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Look how helpless you are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:50.35,ED-eg,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I can see what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:52.39,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Why don't you take my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:53.69,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Take my helping hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.18,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I must be the hero
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:57.35,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}All eyes on me strong and grand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.98,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I must be the greater
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:00.61,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I must be the savior
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:02.53,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}All eyes on me here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:04.49,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}They say I'm their messiah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:06.12,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}All of the hopes and dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:07.86,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Are in this broken tambourine
