Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:11.66,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Like how it used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:13.69,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Come witness the birth of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:14.99,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}The greatest loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:17.25,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}In this hollow stillness now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:19.04,ED-eg1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Tell me what will you choose
